					Dr. Rachel Harsley Receives 2017 UIC Distinguished Service Award			</td>
	
	
	
		</tr>
</table>
<table class="contentpaneopen">




<tr>
<td valign="top" colspan="2">
<p>Dr. Rachel Harsley, NLP Lab alumna, was awarded the 2017 UIC Distinguished Service Award by the Engineering Alumni Association. The award was bestowed on November 15, 2017, at the UIC College of Engineering Alumni Awards Dinner.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><img src="/images/photos/rachel-uic-award-2017.jpg" border="0" alt="Dr. Rachel Harsley and Dr. Barbara Di Eugenio" width="300" height="500" /></p></td>
</tr>

