		<td class="contentheading" width="100%">
					Nick Green defends his PhD thesis (March 2, 2017)			</td>
	
	
	
		</tr>
</table>
<table class="contentpaneopen">




<tr>
<td valign="top" colspan="2">
<p>Nick Green successfully defended his PhD thesis, titled: "Example Based Pedagogical Strategies in a Computer Science Intelligent Tutoring System"</p>
<p>His committee included: Barbara Di Eugenio (advisor), Tom Moher (CS, UIC), Ugo Buy (CS, UIC), Davide Fossati (CS, Emory University), Patrick Seeling (CS, Central Michigan University)</p>
<p><img src="/images/photos/nick_phd_defense.jpg" border="0" width="400" height="300" /></p></td>
</tr>

